{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-yongfeng-007__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-007", "source_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄘風·007.1", "text_original": "蝃蝀在東，莫之敢指，女子有行，遠父母兄弟。", "text_normalized": "蝃蝀在東，莫之敢指，女子有行，遠父母兄弟。", "notes": "蝃蝀 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-yongfeng-007__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-007", "source_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄘風·007.2", "text_original": "朝隮于西，崇朝其雨，女子有行，遠兄弟父母。", "text_normalized": "朝隮于西，崇朝其雨，女子有行，遠兄弟父母。", "notes": "蝃蝀 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-yongfeng-007__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-007", "source_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄘風·007.3", "text_original": "乃如之人也，懷昏姻也，大無信也，不知命也。", "text_normalized": "乃如之人也，懷昏姻也，大無信也，不知命也。", "notes": "蝃蝀 Chinese stanza 3."}
